            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">Book a domestic One-way/Roundtrip flight for 3 or more passengers using coupon code <span class="offer-code"><a href="JavaScript:Void(0)" class="offer_book_now" >CTFLAT500</a> and get Flat ₹ 500 Off. </span>  <br />  <br />
